NOTICE - CLINICAL USE: DrJSK AfterCare is an AI-assisted post-visit patient
care platform in pilot for the practice of Dr James Southwell-Keely
(drjsk.com.au). It provides general post-operative guidance only and is NOT a
substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. It does
not provide emergency care. Patients who are concerned must contact the
practice on (02) 9369 2800, and in an emergency call 000. Clinical content is
reviewed by the treating surgeon; use of this software does not create a
doctor-patient relationship on its own. This software is derived under the MIT
License from the PostVisit.ai hackathon prototype (Built with Opus 4.6,
February 2026).
